      <p class="para" style="font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:8px;">Demographics (study-relevant only)</p>
      <ul class="criteria-list">
        <li class="criteria-item">Currently employed as a full-time or part-time store associate, supervisor, or team leader at a Next store in the UK or Ireland</li>
        <li class="criteria-item">Primary role involves regular POS till operation — not warehouse, stock room, or head office only</li>
        <li class="criteria-item">Mix of store sizes where possible (small high street, large out-of-town format)</li>
        <li class="criteria-item">Mix of tenure — at least 2 participants with less than 12 months tenure; at least 3 with 2+ years tenure</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="para" style="font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:8px;margin-top:12px;">Qualifying Criteria</p>
      <ul class="criteria-list">
        <li class="criteria-item">Has operated the POS till as their primary work activity at a Next store in the past 30 days</li>
        <li class="criteria-item">Has processed a customer return at the till in the past 60 days</li>
        <li class="criteria-item">Has introduced or explained an in-store promotion or new service to a customer at the till in the past 90 days</li>
        <li class="criteria-item">Has not been involved in the planning or design of the Next loyalty programme in any professional capacity</li>
        <li class="criteria-item">Is comfortable being interviewed remotely and has access to a stable internet connection for a video call</li>
