            <div class="sq-opt">I have never worked at Next <span class="tag tag-reject">[Reject]</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="screener-q">
          <div class="sq-num">SQ2</div>
          <div class="sq-text">In the past 30 days, how often has operating the POS till been part of your shift?</div>
          <div class="sq-options">
            <div class="sq-opt">Every shift or almost every shift <span class="tag tag-accept">[Must Accept]</span></div>
            <div class="sq-opt">More than half my shifts <span class="tag tag-accept">[Must Accept]</span></div>
            <div class="sq-opt">Occasionally — less than half my shifts <span class="tag tag-may">[May Accept — limit to 2]</span></div>
            <div class="sq-opt">I have not operated the till in the past 30 days <span class="tag tag-reject">[Reject]</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="screener-q">
          <div class="sq-num">SQ3</div>
          <div class="sq-text">Have you processed a customer return at the till in the past 60 days?</div>
          <div class="sq-options">
            <div class="sq-opt">Yes, multiple times <span class="tag tag-accept">[Must Accept]</span></div>
            <div class="sq-opt">Yes, at least once <span class="tag tag-accept">[Must Accept]</span></div>
            <div class="sq-opt">No <span class="tag tag-reject">[Reject]</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="screener-q">
          <div class="sq-num">SQ4</div>
          <div class="sq-text">In the past 90 days, have you introduced or explained an in-store promotion, new service, or company initiative to a customer at the till?</div>
