            <div class="sq-opt">Yes, this has been part of my role recently <span class="tag tag-accept">[Must Accept]</span></div>
            <div class="sq-opt">Not in the past 90 days, but it has been part of my role in the past <span class="tag tag-may">[May Accept — limit to 2]</span></div>
            <div class="sq-opt">No, this has not been part of my role <span class="tag tag-reject">[Reject]</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>

